<article class="info relative isolate py-8 flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-start">
  <div class="prose dark:prose-invert lg:w-2/3 py-4 ml-4">
    <div class="relative isolate origin-top transition-all duration-75 grid content-start grid-rows-[auto_1fr_auto] text-xl bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700" id="status-container">
      <div class="relative">
        <button class="absolute -left-[.9em] h-full transition duration-75" id="toggle-button">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-muted-foreground/50 hover:text-muted-foreground arrow-icon rotate-0">
            <path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"></path>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <span class="font-mono text-muted-foreground/70 text-white">&lt;</span>
        <span class="font-mono font-semibold text-accent text-violet-500"  data-translate="status.title">Estatus</span>
        <span class="font-mono text-muted-foreground/70 text-white">&gt;</span>
      </div>
      <div id="status-content" class="border-l-2 border-muted-foreground/50 pl-8 text-gray-300 overflow-hidden hover:border-muted-foreground hidden">
        <div class="py-4 font-mono">
          <p class="m-0 p-0 text-muted-foreground" data-translate="status.content" >
            Actualmente en busca de oportunidades desafiantes para continuar expandiendo mis habilidades, comprometido con el aprendizaje de nuevas tecnologías y marcos.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-xl">
      <span class="font-mono text-muted-foreground/70 text-white">&lt;/</span>
      <span class="font-mono font-semibold text-accent text-violet-500"  data-translate="status.title">Estatus</span>
      <span class="font-mono text-muted-foreground/70 text-white">&gt;</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto size-fit lg:ml-8">
    <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-4 mb-3 dark:bg-gray-700 text-white hover:shadow-violet-800 hover:shadow-lg md:hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
      <p class="text-base font-normal"  data-translate="hobbies.content">
        Disfruto de los videojuegos y en un futuro crear mi propio videojuego, cocinar y hacer ejercicio.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-4 mb-3 dark:bg-gray-700 text-white hover:shadow-violet-800 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 md:hover:scale-105">
      <p class="text-base font-normal"  data-translate="skills.content">
        Como desarrollador de software, mis conocimientos técnicos se basan en una amplia gama de herramientas, lenguajes y marcos de trabajo que me permiten dar vida a soluciones digitales.
      </p>
    </div>
    </div>
  </article>
  
  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      const toggleButton = document.getElementById('toggle-button');
      const statusContent = document.getElementById('status-content');
      const arrowIcon = toggleButton.querySelector(".arrow-icon");
      const statusContainer = document.getElementById('status-container');
  
      toggleButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
        statusContent.classList.toggle('hidden');
        arrowIcon.classList.toggle('rotate-0');
        arrowIcon.classList.toggle('rotate-90');
        statusContainer.classList.toggle('bg-gray-900');
        statusContainer.classList.toggle('dark:bg-gray-700');
      });
    });
  </script>
  
  <style>
    .hidden {
      display: none;
    }
    .rotate-0 {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
      transition: transform 0.5s ease;
    }
    .rotate-90 {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      transition: transform 0.5s ease;
    }
  </style>